This paper deals with machine learning algorithms and hyperparameter tuning, which are common topics in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper's focus on meta-learning and its application to different datasets also suggests that it could fit into these sub-categories.
